



# THE WAY FORWARD

## A Strategic Evolution for Large-Scale AI

### A Proposal for Integrating Deterministic Edge AI with Future High-Performance Computing

---

## 1. The Opportunity

Artificial intelligence has reached an extraordinary milestone. Large stochastic language models have demonstrated capabilities that were unimaginable only a few years ago. They have transformed research, software development, education, healthcare, and countless other fields.

At the same time, their success has revealed new engineering challenges. As AI adoption accelerates worldwide, questions surrounding energy consumption, latency, infrastructure costs, data sovereignty, and predictable execution are becoming increasingly important. These challenges do not diminish the achievements of modern AI—they define the next stage of its evolution.

**ST-T1024** is presented as one possible contribution to addressing these challenges. Rather than replacing existing AI ecosystems, we propose exploring how deterministic embedded inference can complement cloud-based intelligence.

---

