| **Energy** | Cloud AI consumes >1,000 TWh by 2030 | 99.9% reduction via edge inference |
| **Latency** | 50 ms cloud round-trip | 680 ns deterministic response |
| **Sovereignty** | Data exported to foreign clouds | Air-gapped, sovereign deployment |
